data.title: Spaghetti Measurer
data.meta_description: Features: Measure out perfect portions of spaghetti noodles. It comes with four separate measurements to avoid cooking too much or too little. This spaghetti measure is plastic in form and very easy to clean and store. Great gift idea. Perfect addition to any kitchen. Color shown may not be what is delivered.
data.text:
Features: Measure out perfect portions of spaghetti noodles. It comes with four separate measurements to avoid cooking too much or too little. This spaghetti measure is plastic in form and very easy to clean and store. Great gift idea. Perfect addition to any kitchen.

Color shown may not be what is delivered.
